title: Focus On The Playoff Picture
description:
Laura, Swagu, Dan, and Key breakdown some of the important Week 18 matchups that will impact the upcoming playoffs, discuss how Jalen Hurts has done his job in Philly, and the key offensive line and defensive line matchups for Week 18.
